Hi!
Thank you for a response. I don't know to create a PR. The workaround about this issue that worked for me, was to transform the byte[] values to String, as below:

 private static JavaRDD<Row> rddArrayByteValueToString(JavaRDD<Row> rddByteArrayValues) {
    return rddByteArrayValues.map(row -> {

      scala.collection.Seq<Object> values = row.toSeq();

      Collection<Object> asList = new ArrayList<>(values.size());
      for (scala.collection.Iterator<Object> iterator = values.toList().iterator(); iterator
          .hasNext();) {

        Object v = iterator.next();
        if (v instanceof byte[]) {
          //do you need UTF-8??
          asList.add(new String((byte[]) v));
        } else {
          asList.add(v);
        }
      }
      return RowFactory.create(asList.toArray());
    });

  }

